voicesplitting.generic

  • Packages that use voicesplitting.generic 
    Package Description
    voicesplitting.generic
    Provides abstract classes to guide the creation of MIDI models and their states.

    Provides functionality for performing voice separation.

    Provides the HMM-based voice splitting model which is the main focus of this project.
